s_-_Photo_14_1.png","product_three":"metamorphosis-lushlips-transformation","top-postion3":54,"left-postion3":42,"mobile-top-postion3":55,"mobile-left-postion3":48,"content":"<p>Revolutionary light therapy, masterfully crafted for effortless and effective transformation. Discover your path to timeless beauty with an artful ritual for the modern age.<\/p>","btn":"BEGIN YOUR TRANSFORMATION","url":"shopify:\/\/collections\/all-collection"}},"service_icon_hEBpVU":{"type":"service-icon","blocks":{"item_Kga3Jy":{"type":"item","settings":{"custom_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Frame_2087326400.svg","title":"Clinically-<br>proven results"}},"item_zy8rkD":{"type":"item","settings":{"custom_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_2.svg","title":"ONE YEAR<br>WARRANTY"}},"item_3MQRnk":{"type":"item","settings":{"custom_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_2_1.svg","title":"Dermatologist<br>recommended"}},"item_q7wJpc":{"type":"item","settings":{"custom_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.svg","title":"FDA<br>Cleared"}},"item_q4XbdK":{"type":"item","settings":{"custom_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Asset_1.svg","title":"Self-Timed<br>Treatment"}}},"block_order":["item_Kga3Jy","item_zy8rkD","item_3MQRnk","item_q7wJpc","item_q4XbdK"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"bgcolor":"#ffffff","textcolor":"#828282","paddTop":false,"padBottom":true,"customClass":"","title":"SKINCARE ROOTED IN INNOVATION, <br>PROVEN BY SCIENCE"}},"image_text_btn_section_ftne4d":{"type":"image-text-btn-section","disabled":true,"settings":{"bg_color":"","text_block":"#fafafa","img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Frame_2087326766.png","heading":"A JOURNEY OF TRANSFORMATION","content":"<p>After 30 years as a successful attorney, Sally Gardocki followed her deep passion for beauty tech and wellness, founding Metamorphosis Light Therapy. Inspired by her personal experience, Sally channeled her analytical expertise and passion for cutting-edge innovation into exploring the transformative science of red light therapy. Sally’s fearless reinvention inspires others to embrace change and pursue their own metamorphosis. <br\/><em>Look good. Feel good. Do good.<\/em><\/p>","btn":"START YOUR METAMORPHOSIS","url":"shopify:\/\/collections\/all"}},"testimonials_section_LGVAAk":{"type":"testimonials-section","blocks":{"text_kTHQmJ":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>\"I am in love with my MagicMoon! My undereyes are tighter and smoother after just a few uses. The portable shape makes it the perfect traveling companion to give me a quick refresh and look instantly well-rested..... <\/em><\/p>","rte_content":"<p><em>\"I am in love with my MagicMoon! My undereyes are tighter and smoother after just a few uses. The portable shape makes it the perfect traveling companion to give me a quick refresh and look instantly well-rested. I pop them on when I'm organizing around the house and also when I'm on the go. Super convenient and effective!\" <\/em><\/p>","city_text":"Ellie, Naples","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.png"}},"text_QTV8qq":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>\"I've never used a red light product in my life, but the fact that the MagicMoon is so easy to use and well researched, without me having to invest too much made them a 10\/10 for me.  I recommend it!\"<\/em><\/p>","rte_content":"","city_text":"Jannar, New York City","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.png"}},"text_EqaVYa":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>“I started using the LushLips every night as part of my nighttime routine. I have always been insecure about the small size of my lips, but even after only using these for a short time, my lips already look smoother and plumper!.........<\/em><\/p>","rte_content":"<p><em>“I started using the LushLips every night as part of my nighttime routine. I have always been insecure about the small size of my lips, but even after only using these for a short time, my lips already look smoother and plumper! They are so comfortable and easy to use, and I can’t believe they make such a difference in only 3 minutes. I can’t go an evening without using them now!”<\/em><\/p>","city_text":"Julia, Louisiana","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.png"}},"text_XWRtLU":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>“I’ve been dealing with melasma and hyperpigmentation for a few years and recently took the plunge on laser facials and started using the red lights on areas I wanted to target in between sessions and have seen pretty incredible results so far!.<\/em><\/p>","rte_content":"<p><em>“I’ve been dealing with melasma and hyperpigmentation for a few years and recently took the plunge on laser facials and started using the red lights on areas I wanted to target in between sessions and have seen pretty incredible results so far! And I’m glad I found these MagicMoon as I can continue to use them as upkeep which is also way more affordable than laser.  The hydrogel MagicMoon eye patches are a great combo to use after the treatment, and I like to put them in the fridge for extra cooling effect, especially in the morning.  It’s a nice little selfcare routine ☺  I wish I started this sooner!” <\/em><\/p>","city_text":"Jena, New York City","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.png"}},"text_EntmXA":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>“The LushLips hydrogel mask is a game changer for my lips! It provides immediate hydration, leaving my lips feeling incredibly soft and smooth. I always use these when my lips are feeling dry or after being in the sun for a while!....<\/em><\/p>","rte_content":"<p><em>“The LushLips hydrogel mask is a game changer for my lips! It provides immediate hydration, leaving my lips feeling incredibly soft and smooth. I always use these when my lips are feeling dry or after being in the sun for a while! The lip masks fit perfectly without slipping, unlike other lip masks I’ve tried that fall down my face. After just one use, my lips feel rejuvenated.”<\/em><\/p><p><em>Also, “SuperStar red light pimple patches are absolutely amazing! And this is unlike any other pimple patches, because you don’t have to leave it on for hours to see results! It significantly reduces the size and redness of my pimples right after use! It is so easy to use and the effective results have made it an everyday staple in my skincare routine.  I can’t believe how quickly it can clear up my skin! Also, it came in the cutest packaging and is so easy to bring with you anywhere you go! Definitely my new go-to pimple patch!”<\/em><\/p>","city_text":"Tory, Washington, DC","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.png"}},"text_x6PcEt":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>“The search for the perfect eye treatment is now over! Metamorphosis MagicMoon Eye Evolution is a game changer! Actually, it is a life changer! Nothing has come close to the remarkable results I’ve experienced in a short amount.....<\/em><\/p>","rte_content":"<p><em>“The search for the perfect eye treatment is now over! Metamorphosis MagicMoon Eye Evolution is a game changer! Actually, it is a life changer! Nothing has come close to the remarkable results I’ve experienced in a short amount of time (a couple of weeks) and requires no needles, no downtime and can be done at any time of the day.  They are engineered with convenience in mind: rechargeable, easy to clean, small enough to fit into a makeup bag or handbag. I couldn’t be more thrilled with the results. I can stop wasting time and money with eye treatments, creams or procedures.  MagicMoon gives me the youthful, refreshed appearance I’ve always wanted in just 3 minutes per day!”<\/em><\/p><p><em>Also:  “Aging can do cruel things to a woman’s body.  Slight changes happen over time. One day, you look in the mirror and hardly recognize the face staring back at you.  This was the case with my lips.  Small lines and thinning set in, and being needle adverse, I thought I would just have to live with it.  LushLips has saved the day though!  Having personally experienced Magic Moons, I am sold on the company, so investing in LushLips was a no-brainer.  After 2 weeks, I can tell a difference! Small lines are disappearing, the corners of my mouth are softening and this is without any needles or downtime!  LushLips takes 3 minutes, is painless and revives my lips!”<\/em><\/p>","city_text":"Diane, Atlanta","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Layer_1.png"}}},"block_order":["text_kTHQmJ","text_QTV8qq","text_EqaVYa","text_XWRtLU","text_EntmXA","text_x6PcEt"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"background-img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/image_161.png","text_color":"#ffffff","tite":"TESTIMONIALS"}},"cus_img_banner_section_fdgwwx":{"type":"cus-img-banner-section","disabled":true,"settings":{"back_color":"#ffffff","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2111728336786__2_4.png"}},"shop_by_category_4ayVq8":{"type":"shop-by-category","blocks":{"image_picker_VHrH4g":{"type":"image_picker","settings":{"img_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/led-light-devices","image_category":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Metamorphosis_-_PDP_Silicone_Patches.png","title_caption":"LED DEVICES","text_color":"#696969"}},"image_picker_t7AN6j":{"type":"image_picker","settings":{"img_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/hydrogel-masks","image_category":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Metamorphosis_-_PDP_Silicone_Patches_-_Update_3_images_for__Shop_by_category.png","title_caption":"HYDROGEL MASKS","text_color":"#696969"}},"image_picker_Fr8dDG":{"type":"image_picker","settings":{"img_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/sculpt-lift","image_category":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Metamorphosis-red-gift-bag-butterfly-gifting-packaging.png","title_caption":"SCULPT AND LIFT KIT","text_color":"#696969"}}},"block_order":["image_picker_VHrH4g","image_picker_t7AN6j","image_picker_Fr8dDG"],"settings":{"padding_top":true,"padding_bottom":false,"back_color":"#ffffff","heading_color":"#000000","text_color":"#000000","shop_title":"SHOP BY CATEGORY","sub_text":"Discover the art of transformation with our cutting-edge collection.  From the rejuvenating power of LEDs to deeply nourishing and targeted hydrogel masks and the sculpting precision of our lift kit, each creation is designed to work in perfect harmony.","btn_text":"SHOP ALL DEVICES","btn_url":"shopify:\/\/collections\/led-light-devices"}},"blog_slider_section_YKhTPn":{"type":"blog-slider-section","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"LATEST BLOGS","blog":"blog-1","post_limit":3,"show_image":true,"show_date":true}},"newsletter":{"type":"newsletter","disabled":true,"custom_css":[],"settings":{"back_color":"#fafafa","heading":"","heading_animation":true,"sub_title":"LET YOUR NATURAL BEAUTY SHINE!","newsletter_text":"Have a question, suggestion, or inquiry? We're all ears!<br>Drop a message and start a conversation. <br>\u2028Your thoughts are important to us,  <br>and we promise to respond with the same enthusiasm.","button_style":"secondary","border_top":false}}},"order":["home_banner_section_NREwEY","icon_text_bar_876xXU","featured_in_section_DUBX6G","feature_testimonial_dARD6b","clinically_verified_results_p8P4zz","cosmoprof_awards_section_98F4VJ","new_home_collection_grid_WAb8Ft","skincare_grid_section_Tyrnte","video_loop_section_GrkrER","your_result_GWmgLg","new_home_collection_grid_DYGxRm","skincare_grid_section_Bw3LaY","service_icon_ipqeXx","how_it_works_section_UKn8pA","img_tooltip_section_rg3FFt","service_icon_hEBpVU","image_text_btn_section_ftne4d","testimonials_section_LGVAAk","cus_img_banner_section_fdgwwx","shop_by_category_4ayVq8","blog_slider_section_YKhTPn","newsletter"]}